Reasoning: The paper focuses on performance analysis and efficient execution of a microscopy image analysis application on different computing devices, including multi-core CPUs, GPUs, and Intel Xeon Phi (Many Integrated Core - MIC). This involves aspects of distributed computing (cs.DC), computer vision (cs.CV), augmented reality (cs.AR), numerical analysis (cs.NA), and control systems (cs.SY).
